sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Gradio App
    participant RAG as OllamaRAG
    participant VS as SimpleVectorStore
    participant OC as OllamaClient

    Note over User,OC: === P1-7: RAG 一键索引 ===

    User->>UI: 点击 "📚 索引 docs 目录"
    UI->>RAG: OllamaRAG()
    RAG->>RAG: _check_embed_model()
    UI->>RAG: index_documents("./docs")
    RAG->>RAG: 遍历 docs/ (*.md, *.txt, *.pdf)
    loop 每个文件
        RAG->>RAG: _chunk_text(content)
        RAG->>RAG: _get_embedding(chunk)
        RAG->>VS: add_chunk(chunk, doc_id)
    end
    RAG->>VS: _save_index()
    RAG-->>UI: chunk_count
    UI->>RAG: get_stats()
    RAG-->>UI: {total_documents, total_chunks}
    UI-->>User: "✅ 索引完成"

    Note over User,OC: === P1-7: RAG 简答模式 ===

    User->>UI: 勾选"简答模式" + 提问
    UI->>UI: rag_query(q, top_k, simple=True)
    UI->>OC: OllamaClient(MODEL_DOC)
    OC->>OC: generate("请回答：{q}", temp=0.3)
    OC-->>UI: answer
    UI-->>User: 回答内容

    Note over User,OC: === P1-10: 知识图谱文件上传 ===

    User->>UI: 上传文档 + 点击构建图谱
    UI->>UI: build_knowledge_graph(text_input, file_obj)
    UI->>UI: save_file(file_obj)
    UI->>UI: parser.parse(file_path)
    UI->>UI: doc.content
    UI->>UI: KnowledgeGraphBuilder.extract_from_text()
    UI-->>User: 图谱结果（实体+关系+Mermaid）

    Note over User,OC: === P1-11: 增强模式 Agent ===

    User->>UI: 点击 "⚡ 增强模式 (Harness)"
    UI->>UI: multi_agent_enhanced(task, agents, context)
    UI->>UI: EnhancedCOMACAssistant()
    UI->>UI: harness = AdvancedHarness(config)

    loop 每个选中的 Agent
        UI->>UI: _build_agent_prompt(agent, task, context)
        UI->>UI: harness.execute_with_harness(task, llm_call, context)
        UI->>OC: llm_call(prompt) [Self-Correction]
        OC-->>UI: generated text
    end

    UI-->>User: 格式化的多 Agent 输出 [增强模式]
